+@captain @conformance
+Feature: Methodology conformance
+  Methodology checks so Shipshape method violations surface as
+  failing verification.
+
+  @captain @conformance
+  Scenario: Perturbation quiescence
+    Given the project has been scanned for perturbation tokens
+    When the implementation source tree is searched for the text "PERTURBATION"
+    Then no match is found
+
+  @captain @conformance
+  Scenario: Plank form is valid
+    Given every @planks annotation in the implementation directories
+    When each annotation string is checked against the step-usage patterns
+    Then every @planks string matches a current step-definition pattern exactly
+    And every @planks-provisional reference names a @captain scenario that still exists
+
+  @captain @conformance
+  Scenario: No forbidden test doubles
+    Given the verification support code
+    When it is scanned for test doubles
+    Then every double carries an @exceptional-double inline mark
